text: Javesella is a genus of delphacid planthoppers in the family Delphacidae. There are at least 20 described species in Javesella. ==Species== These 24 species belong to the genus Javesella. ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * * * * * * * * * * * Category:Auchenorrhyncha genera Category:Delphacini
